1
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:48,700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:51,780
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:58,039 --> 00:00:58,759
Today,

4
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,560
we're definitely going to win.

5
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:01,759
I really didn't expect it.

6
00:01:02,159 --> 00:01:03,640
Xiao Group was almost going bankrupt,

7
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:06,280
but they've managed to latch onto Dihao.

8
00:01:06,399 --> 00:01:07,000
I heard

9
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,240
the eldest heiress, Xiao Churan,
landed the deal.

10
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,480
I wonder what she did.

11
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,439
You don't know?

12
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:14,359
It was Mr. Zhang Wenhao
who set up the meeting.

13
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,719
Why would he help her?

14
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:18,719
What else could it be?

15
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,239
I get it now.

16
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:24,359
But doesn't she have a husband?

17
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,760
That useless guy?

18
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,599
If it were me,

19
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,200
I'd pick Mr. Zhang too.

20
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,840
Later, Ms. Wang is going

21
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,380
to slap Zhang Wenhao in the face.

22
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,000
This place is nice.

23
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,879
Quit acting here.

24
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,480
Churan,

25
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,560
you should talk some sense into him.

26
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:54,120
It's still not too late to admit defeat.

27
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,780
What did you say?

28
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:57,799
I can't hear you with the mask on.

29
00:01:58,079 --> 00:02:00,359
I heard ice packs
help with swelling faster.

30
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,719
Reverse.

31
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,120
Grandma,

32
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,680
look at the time.

33
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,319
Ye Chen,

34
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,360
is Ms. Wang really coming?

35
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,120
Not only has Ms. Wang not come,

36
00:02:30,230 --> 00:02:31,599
but none of Dihao's representatives

37
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,719
have shown up either.

38
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,520
Did they get played?

39
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:38,680
Ye Chen,

40
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:39,840
just admit defeat.

41
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:43,120
Ms. Wang won't be coming today.

42
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,360
Ye Chen, how dare you?

43
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:47,280
Are you trying to ruin our family?

44
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:50,199
Don't worry. If I say Dongxue will come,

45
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,360
she'll definitely come.

46
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,639
Get out, now!

47
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,879
- Get out!
- Get out!

48
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:56,039
- You hear us?
- Hurry up!

49
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,660
You hear us?

50
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:00,360
Ye Chen,

51
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,360
aren't you going to leave?

52
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,439
Stop embarrassing our family.

53
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,120
Seriously.

54
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,039
Wait.

55
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,360
Get on your knees first.

56
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,159
Exactly.

57
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,599
Ye Chen,

58
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,039
a bet's a bet.

59
00:03:12,050 --> 00:03:13,280
Do you need me to help you out?

60
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,080
She's here!

61
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:23,759
She's here.

62
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,000
Ms. Wang's here.

63
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,639
(Perfect timing.)

64
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,000
- Don't move!
- Stop!

65
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,500
Stay still.

66
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:52,599
Mr. Hong.

67
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:57,759
I've got more numbers.

68
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,690
Zhang Wenhao did this.

69
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,919
He sent me here.

70
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:00,759
Get him.

71
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,000
Move!

72
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,240
Ms. Wang.

73
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,599
Thank you, Mr. Hong.

74
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:05,960
Why are you here?

75
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,400
I'm Ye Chen's friend.

76
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:08,880
He sent me to keep an eye on things.

77
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,439
Thank you.

78
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,719
Ms. Wang,

79
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,759
welcome.

80
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:21,080
Ms. Xiao, Mr. Ye,

81
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,879
sorry I came late.

82
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,360
Ms. Wang, you're too kind.

83
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,759
Ms. Wang,
it's an honor to have you here.

84
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,399
Ms. Wang,

85
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,920
shall we head upstairs?

86
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:35,120
Ms. Wang, you're not only capable
but also young and pretty.

87
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,639
Exactly.

88
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,360
Ouch.

89
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,200
I can't feel my arm.

90
00:04:39,210 --> 00:04:40,560
This show is just getting started.

91
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,190
You're leaving?

92
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,240
Since you care so much about Churan,

93
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,199
how can you not witness

94
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,240
her big moment together?

95
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,199
Come on.

96
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,319
Ms. Wang,

97
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,639
here's to a great partnership.

98
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,240
Shall we begin now?

99
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,720
Wait a minute.

100
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:56,439
I think

101
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:59,800
Ms. Xiao Churan
should represent Xiao Group

102
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,199
to sign this contract.

103
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,480
It's thanks to her excellent proposal

104
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:05,000
that we chose to work with Xiao Group.

105
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:07,079
Grandma,

106
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,839
did you forget something?

107
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:12,060
(Jinxi Resort Strategic Partnership
Signing Ceremony)

108
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,160
Oh, right.

109
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,319
I can't believe I forgot.

110
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,120
Everyone,

111
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,199
I'd like to take

112
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,360
this moment to announce

113
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,720
that I will propose to the board

114
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,600
to appoint Xiao Churan

115
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,399
as the Chief Operating Officer

116
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,759
of Xiao Group.

117
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,600
Sit still.

118
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:36,100
(Dihao Group Jinxi Resort
Project Agreement)

119
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,180
(Dihao Group, Wang Dongxue,
Xiao Group, Xiao Churan)

120
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,360
Thank you, Ms. Wang.

121
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,279
Stop right there.

122
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,519
- Grandma.
- Grandma.

123
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,120
Get up.

124
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,399
Look at yourself.

125
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,120
I'm getting old.

126
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,720
Watching you youngsters do so well,

127
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:07,879
I think it's time I step down.

128
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,800
I will propose to the board

129
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:13,279
to appoint Xiao Hailong
as the chairperson of Xiao Group

130
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,319
and Xiao Weiwei as the CEO.

131
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,920
They'll lead Xiao Churan and the others

132
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,519
and be fully responsible
for the partnership with Dihao Group.

133
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,399
Grandma, you used us
and just threw us away?

134
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:27,800
You...

135
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,240
You heartless witch.

136
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:31,560
I disagree.

137
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,220
As long as Grandma is here,

138
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,279
it's not your turn
to manage the Xiao family.

139
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:36,120
Exactly.

140
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,639
What are you even?

141
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,240
Ms. Wang,

142
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,319
do you agree?

143
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,519
Of course, I don't agree.

144
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:45,720
Ms. Wang,

145
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,720
I'm doing this

146
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,759
for the reputation
of both our companies.

147
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:51,240
At Dihao Group,

148
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,160
we only care about Ms. Xiao Churan.

149
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,220
In the future,

150
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,519
we'll only be dealing with her.

151
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:00,399
If you want to push forward
with your personnel changes,

152
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,839
then I'm sorry,

153
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,759
but I'll have
to terminate the partnership.

154
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:07,199
But we've already signed the contract.

155
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,600
I can afford the penalty fee.

156
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,680
However, from now on, Dihao Group

157
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,160
will join forces with all our friends

158
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:15,199
to completely blacklist Xiao Group.

159
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,680
I announce that the previous
appointments are void.

160
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:31,920
Xiao Group will be led
by Xiao Churan as the chairperson.

161
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:35,279
She'll be fully responsible
for the partnership with Dihao.

162
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,439
Nice!

163
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,959
- Grandma.
- Grandma.

164
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,360
Save your breath.

165
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,279
You'd better think
about how to kneel later.

166
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:47,240
You two were the ones
who insisted on betting with me.

167
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,000
A bet's a bet.

168
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,920
What do you think, Grandma?

169
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,730
Get on your knees.

170
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,399
Grandma.

171
00:07:59,319 --> 00:07:59,800
Wait.

172
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:01,279
Don't kneel just yet.

173
00:08:03,650 --> 00:08:04,079
Sit here.

174
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,079
The coronation ceremony has to be grand.

175
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,480
Now you can kneel.

176
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,399
Wait.

177
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,519
This is such an important occasion.

178
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,959
We have to get a photo.

179
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,000
Alright.

180
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,600
Congratulations, Ms. Xiao.

181
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,360
Thank you.

182
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,680
Ms. Xiao,
let's work together in the future.

183
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:33,519
I got to say,

184
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,879
thank you for today.

185
00:08:35,319 --> 00:08:36,480
You were really cool.

186
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,519
Well, I won't see you off.

187
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,519
Alright, bye.

188
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,000
Did you see

189
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,039
Mr. Zhang's face just now? What a sight.

190
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,080
It's all thanks to Ye Chen.

191
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,200
Churan, can you take
Mom and Dad home first?

192
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,570
I've got something to take care of.

193
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,240
Alright.

194
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,000
Be careful.

195
00:08:53,690 --> 00:08:55,120
Just kicking him while he's down.

196
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,240
Mom, Dad, take care.

197
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,279
Who did he mean?

198
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,320
No one. Let's go.

199
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:03,000
Alright, let's go.

200
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,519
Guys, thanks for your hard work.

201
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,000
Chen.

202
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:10,039
Chen, you're too polite.

203
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,759
We're going back to report to Mr. Hong.

204
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,279
Give him my regards.

205
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:13,720
Sure thing.

206
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,240
- We're leaving now.
- Thanks.

207
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,320
How was that?

208
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,919
Wasn't that a great show?

209
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,559
Did you enjoy it?

210
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,480
Ye Chen,

211
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:26,399
don't get too cocky.

212
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:28,000
Our issue isn't over yet.

213
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:28,919
Zhang Wenhao,

214
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:31,120
you and your family are done for.

215
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,080
Ye Chen,

216
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:37,840
my family might not
compare to Dihao Group,

217
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:40,120
but we're still
one of the top in Jinzhou.

218
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,159
We've got a big business.

219
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,480
You can't just say we're done for.

220
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,600
Who do you think you are?

221
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,780
(Dad)

222
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,159
Answer it.

223
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,519
There might be a surprise.

224
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,679
Yes, Dad?

225
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,120
You troublemaker!

226
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,720
What did you do on earth?

227
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,200
Dihao Group just told me

228
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:06,240
they're terminating
all partnerships with our family!

229
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,799
Now all the shareholders

230
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,519
are dumping our stocks.

231
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,320
You've ruined

232
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,440
our decades of hard work!

233
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,559
Dad, wait.

234
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,080
You're not my son!

235
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:15,480
I...

236
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:22,679
Mr. Ye.

237
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,360
Mr. Ye, I'm sorry.

238
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,159
I surrender.

239
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:27,559
Mr. Ye,

240
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,720
please have mercy on me.

241
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,960
Please spare my family.

242
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:34,519
I have two important women in my life.

243
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,440
One is Madam Li,

244
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,840
and the other is Churan.

245
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,080
You kept Madam Li from getting surgery.

246
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,990
You harassed Churan
and spread rumors about her.

247
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,559
I might forgive anyone in my life,
but not you.

248
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,080
Mr. Zhang,

249
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,159
see you next time.

250
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,080
Wait, no.

251
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,919
I hope I never see you again.

252
00:10:57,860 --> 00:11:00,620
♪I belong to no one♪

253
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:04,140
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

254
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:07,260
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

255
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:12,020
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪

256
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:50,748
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

257
00:11:50,835 --> 00:11:54,588
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

258
00:11:55,048 --> 00:11:59,985
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

259
00:12:00,148 --> 00:12:02,435
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

260
00:12:02,748 --> 00:12:05,428
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

261
00:12:06,498 --> 00:12:09,123
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

262
00:12:09,423 --> 00:12:12,435
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

263
00:12:12,635 --> 00:12:15,685
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

264
00:12:15,798 --> 00:12:18,760
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

265
00:12:19,028 --> 00:12:22,185
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

266
00:12:22,410 --> 00:12:26,160
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

267
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:29,023
♪I belong to no one♪

268
00:12:29,085 --> 00:12:32,535
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

269
00:12:32,535 --> 00:12:35,210
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

270
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:41,548
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
